metadata.name: ai_001
metadata.description:
ai_001 is the first AI generated image transferred onto Wet Plate Collodion. Wet Plate Collodion is one of the earliest forms of chemical photography ever discovered in the 1850s. This contact is bringing together the deep past and the far future by fusing AI + Alchemy. 


Wet Plate Collodion is traditionally used in antique portraiture. Now with the darkroom emergence of ai_001 we can look at our future through this historic process blurring the borders of time and space. 


1/1  
ZEITWEITZ  
2022

Generative AI, Wet Plate Collodion
